  "title": "ACCOUNTS ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p>Job Descriptions</p><ul><li>Manage day to day duties of Accounts payables and Accounts receivables </li><li>Processing incoming funds and resolving accounts queries </li><li>Prepare and send statement of accounts to customers </li><li>Prepare monthly payment to vendors and furnish tax deduction details </li><li>Perform collection and credit control </li><li>Any other duties as assigned by reporting superior </li></ul><p>Job Requirements</p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in an accounts or finance role, preferable in the logistics industry</li><li>Strong attention to detail and ability to maintain accurate financial records</li><li>Proficient in using accounting software and Microsoft Office suite, particularly Excel</li><li>Good problem-solving and analytical skills to interact with various stakeholders</li><li>Qualifications in Accounting, Finance, or a related field</li></ul>",
